#3

without column annotation:-exactly same as properties with capital letters

with column annotation:-exactly same as column annotation with capital letters(column annotation name high priority)


#4

true,false,null ----------------->all are small letters


#5

Annotations:- naming conventions like class name

attribute key: naming conventions like method name
